## About the project
Review work  to find remainng  fossil fuel based on countrywise consumption  and Co2 emission 
data of the world. The data from this study were taken from EDGAR (emission database 
for global atmospheric research) & BP statistics for a period from 2000 to 2017 in study.


## tool use

R software,R studio,MS Excel,google sheet,Awesome table

## Finding
finding based on dataset in study concluded that remaining fossil fuel will last for 75 years  

